column10:
I tried for 76 minutes to fix this game, but every time I attempted to play one of the following happened:
-My screen went black and my computer froze completely, forcing me to manually shut it down;
-The first cutscene slowed to a halt, and then froze like I mentioned previously;
-The game kept making my mouse pop up which stopped any of my inputs ever couple seconds, be it in the menus or in the tutorial area.

Great character creator though and weapon movesets, seems like an extremely fun game, if only it bothered working.

+ Not easy but playable: not best souls-like but still a very good and entertaining game with a lot of loot and customization;
+ More like a good DLC to Nioh, but if you didn't play Nioh - best start to play after Nioh 2 main compaign and before Nioh 2 DLC;
+ Boss skills rock: katana is my favorite up to Underworld and Depth;
+ Ninjutsu was improved and expanded, looks amazing;
+ Great with gamepad;

- Demon form sucks;
- Plot is kinda better but still goes by surface, not epic;
- Some features and weapons added for casuals.
